<i>Posted by Moiraine on 05-24-2003 05:56 AM:</i>

<p><b> </b></p>

<p>The calendar was created for the community. The community has made it work for all these years. And now, the community has decided that it is time for Hate to be removed from the calendar. They did so in a manner that mature, with discussion and points of view. The only outstanding issue was when it would actually be removed, and we, as the mods and admins of Berthall, came up with a compromise that most seem willing to accept, even with their reservations.<br />
<br />
Looks to me like they did come together with a sense of harmony. It hasn't disappeared, but is right there.<br />
<br />
And Fear is still on the calendar. For the moment.<!-- BEGIN TEMPLATE: postbit_signature -->
